            . I am clerk to Messrs. Spooner's the bankers.</p>
               <p>Q. Does Mr. Thompson keep cash at your house - A. He draws checks upon us for the credit of the house at Birmingham.</p>
               <p>Q. Look at the signature, 
               <persName id="t18120219-99-person916">
                  John 
                  Thompson
               <interp inst="t18120219-99-person916" type="surname" value="Thompson"></interp>
